setup:
Make sure the CloudWatch Agent is installed on the instance (follow
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonCloudWatch/latest/monitoring/Install-CloudWatch-Agent.html)
then use the following Cloudwatch Agent config:
```json
{
  "agent":
    {
       "run_as_user": "cwagent"
    },
  "metrics":
  {
    "metrics_collected": {
       "disk": {
          "measurement": [
            "used_percent"
          ],
          "resources": [
             "*"
          ],
          "aggregation_dimensions": [
            [ "InstanceId", "path" ]
          ]
       }
     },
    "append_dimensions": {
      "InstanceId": "${aws:InstanceId}"
    }
  }
}
```
